    <text>
        <body>
                <div1>
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a01"/>大魏孝昌三年歲次乙未九月<note n="0066001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30506;＝辛【中研院】</note><app n="0066001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">辛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30506;</rdg></app>酉朔十日
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a02"/>庚午。司州東郡東燕人蔣伯<note n="0066002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30507;＝仙【中研院】</note><app n="0066002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">仙</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30507;</rdg></app>。敬造彌勒石像
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a03"/>一區。清寧天宮。一時俱就。瞻仰嘆曰。 
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a04"/>夫真覺無言。非演說無以詮其旨。應<note n="0066003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30361;＝雖【中研院】</note><app n="0066003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">雖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30361;</rdg></app>隨感。非
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a05"/>真容無以標其見。故捨苦<note n="0066004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02508;＝罔【中研院】</note><app n="0066004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">罔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02508;</rdg></app>若歸心於真應。脩
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a06"/>善莫若精崇於經像。寔以半偈獲投身之感。剋
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a07"/>朝皆成道無疑。如斯微漸。由建解脫於此岸之
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a08"/>下。會無為於彼岸之上。況乃洪<note n="0066005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30508;＝遘【中研院】</note><app n="0066005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">遘</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30508;</rdg></app><note n="0066006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30509;＝顯【中研院】</note><app n="0066006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">顯</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30509;</rdg></app>於大千。麗
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a09"/>造<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">鮮</unclear>於涌塔。茲速出生死於煩<note n="0066007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">惚＝惱【中研院】</note><app n="0066007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">惱</lem><rdg wit="【原】">惚</rdg></app>之<note n="0066008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30510;＝淵【中研院】</note><app n="0066008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">淵</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30510;</rdg></app>。駿入常
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a10"/>樂於我淨之境。自非人通四果。行齊十地。誰能
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a11"/>捨此家珍。崇此奇造也。故佛弟子蔣伯仙。可謂
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a12"/>望挺台岳之標。智通解行之首。結<note n="0066009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30511;＝願【中研院】</note><app n="0066009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">願</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30511;</rdg></app>崇福。咸脩
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a13"/>來善。庶令道齊塵沙。惠充一切。竭己　良粢。造
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a14"/>石像一區。光夫一丈。起子之年。功成　乙未之
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a15"/>末。志力欣齊。應成<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">等</unclear>日。但基廣<note n="0066010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30512;＝營【中研院】</note><app n="0066010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">營</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30512;</rdg></app>高。徐而弗促。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a16"/>尒乃功妙奚方。羨同梵巧。神匠演思。資奇□□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a17"/>冥感。鏤玉錭文。鐫真顏於妙相。明如&CB00222;璃。光□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a18"/>景月。准辰定而置華宇。臨萇湖而□□原。□□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a19"/>紫微勢本<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">洍</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">長</unclear>其尊容□□□□□□□□□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a20"/>宮殿葦曄。若寶塔□□□□□□□□□□□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a21"/>見閻浮祇洹。聖造重顯於今日。觀其□□□□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a22"/>二義之堅。越於五春之茂。僉矚斯妙。□□□□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a23"/>述<note n="0066011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30513;＝敷【中研院】</note><app n="0066011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">敷</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30513;</rdg></app>愚思於<note n="0066012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30512;＝營【中研院】</note><app n="0066012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">營</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30512;</rdg></app>素。勒扶於□石。敬<note n="0066013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30514;＝圖【中研院】</note><app n="0066013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30514;</rdg></app>□□□□。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a24"/>靡惙不能適照。景<note n="0066014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30508;＝遘【中研院】</note><app n="0066014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">遘</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30508;</rdg></app>聊述万一。　　其詞曰。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a25"/>妙哉正覺。應化迦毗。降魔鹿菀。万<note n="0066015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30516;＝蠢【中研院】</note><app n="0066015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">蠢</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30516;</rdg></app>咸歸。廣濟
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a26"/>度訖。雙林漸暉。眾生咸嘆。幽惠&CB08824;<note n="0066016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30515;＝&CB30397;【中研院】</note><app n="0066016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">&CB30397;</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30515;</rdg></app>。嗚吁慈父。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a27"/>有類何往。等為懷情。鐫石<note n="0066017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30514;＝圖【中研院】</note><app n="0066017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30514;</rdg></app>像。不有尊儀。<note n="0066018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30517;＝孰【中研院】</note><app n="0066018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">孰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30517;</rdg></app>
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a28"/>遵孰仰。其一尊<note n="0066019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30519;＝顏【中研院】</note><app n="0066019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">顏</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30519;</rdg></app>奇特。鏤玉錭文。明淨&CB00222;璃。灼□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a29"/>炳分。如月無霄。如日無雲。王宮載生。耆闍□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a30"/>欣。其二宮像葦曄。卜要而安。臨湖<note n="0066020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30141;＝據【中研院】</note><app n="0066020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">據</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30141;</rdg></app>原。清信<note n="0066021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB15137;＝競【中研院】</note><app n="0066021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">競</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB15137;</rdg></app>歡。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a31"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">罕</unclear>遇覆載。妙齊祇洹。緣茲善被。万<note n="0066022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30516;＝蠢【中研院】</note><app n="0066022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">蠢</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30516;</rdg></app>同歡。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0066a32"/>像出梨山。　凡用功三千日。
                </div1>
